description:
Watch The Joy of Seeking God First Episode 6 21-Day Challenge on Vision Video 

"No eye has seen, no ear has heard, no mind has conceived what God has prepared for those who love him." I Corinthians 2:9

The challenge is to request God to teach us what He wants us to know.  To read one Bible chapter a day and to take the time to reflect on what we have read.

Discover the joy of SEEKING GOD FIRST that thousands have already experienced through this powerful, inspiring teaching program led by Anita Keagy, the founder of JoyShop Ministries.

Director: Shane A. Ortiz
Starring: Anita Keagy
tags: The Joy of Seeking God First

chapters.title: Ask God to teach you what He wants you to know.
Take time to reflect on what you read.
Highlight what verses spoke to your heart and why?
What does Jesus want me to know about Him, the Father and the Holy Spirit?
What does Jesus want me to do?
Look for repeated words and phrases.
